show.title: The Fate Is You
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/VEr6g5
show.description: Saved from danger by a mysterious stranger, one man sets out on a determined quest to find and thank his unknown savior. Meanwhile, a family is torn by tension, where a young member is forced to obey elders under threats of punishment. A gripping tale blending mystery, gratitude, and family conflict—where suspense and emotion walk hand in hand.
